1
00:00:33,330 --> 00:00:36,580
♪Flowers falling by the river again♪

2
00:00:36,580 --> 00:00:38,840
♪Turning the clear waves red♪

3
00:00:39,820 --> 00:00:44,600
♪Sparrows singing in celebration♪

4
00:00:46,290 --> 00:00:49,530
♪Calm years pass by the silent bustling city♪

5
00:00:49,530 --> 00:00:52,070
♪Sitting at home♪

6
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:58,260
♪No one knows love's outline like I do♪

7
00:00:58,550 --> 00:01:04,640
♪If one day the river breeze blows again♪

8
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:10,980
♪I won't be a mere reflection in the mirror♪

9
00:01:11,470 --> 00:01:17,540
♪Dreams can shatter; Memories remain♪

10
00:01:17,980 --> 00:01:21,230
♪Rich fragrance aids; Light ink writes♪

11
00:01:21,230 --> 00:01:28,090
♪In the deep red windows lies mundane dust♪

12
00:01:33,260 --> 00:01:40,980
=Are You The One=

13
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:43,980
=Episode 12=

14
00:01:46,750 --> 00:01:47,590
Wait a moment.

15
00:01:52,240 --> 00:01:53,080
Honey.

16
00:01:53,750 --> 00:01:54,960
Do you still remember

17
00:01:54,960 --> 00:01:56,410
that ruffian who impersonated you?

18
00:01:57,700 --> 00:01:58,540
I remember.

19
00:01:58,720 --> 00:01:59,780
Nanny Li said

20
00:02:00,060 --> 00:02:01,220
our marriage certificate

21
00:02:01,220 --> 00:02:02,700
was lost during the move.

22
00:02:03,140 --> 00:02:04,300
I saw the certificate

23
00:02:04,300 --> 00:02:05,220
the ruffian had,

24
00:02:05,740 --> 00:02:07,500
but I didn't find anything unusual.

25
00:02:08,260 --> 00:02:09,220
Thinking it over,

26
00:02:10,340 --> 00:02:11,780
it's probably ours.

27
00:02:13,020 --> 00:02:13,860
It doesn't matter.

28
00:02:14,580 --> 00:02:15,860
How can it not matter?

29
00:02:16,260 --> 00:02:18,380
That's not just a marriage agreement.

30
00:02:18,820 --> 00:02:19,700
It also has

31
00:02:19,700 --> 00:02:21,220
both our names on it.

32
00:02:22,020 --> 00:02:24,020
If it's a man with the same name,

33
00:02:24,180 --> 00:02:25,620
as long as it's not you, Cui Jiu,

34
00:02:25,740 --> 00:02:27,220
it holds no meaning.

35
00:02:28,740 --> 00:02:30,220
I truly hate that scoundrel

36
00:02:30,620 --> 00:02:32,060
for daring to steal your name

37
00:02:32,220 --> 00:02:33,660
and taint our names.

38
00:02:35,180 --> 00:02:37,020
I mean I've asked the authorities.

39
00:02:37,740 --> 00:02:39,220
That marriage certificate isn't ours.

40
00:02:42,140 --> 00:02:43,100
Is that so?

41
00:02:44,500 --> 00:02:46,180
That's a relief.

42
00:02:46,940 --> 00:02:48,900
Don't get upset over this.

43
00:02:49,540 --> 00:02:50,900
You're not healthy enough.

44
00:02:51,980 --> 00:02:53,020
While I'm away,

45
00:02:53,380 --> 00:02:56,020
do more of what you enjoy.

46
00:02:56,980 --> 00:02:58,340
Don't foolishly wait for me.

47
00:02:58,620 --> 00:02:59,460
Okay?

48
00:03:02,820 --> 00:03:03,980
I will.

49
00:03:04,660 --> 00:03:05,940
I'll run the business well,

50
00:03:07,420 --> 00:03:08,500
visit my family,

51
00:03:09,380 --> 00:03:10,260
and wait

52
00:03:12,060 --> 00:03:13,300
for you to return.

53
00:03:18,180 --> 00:03:19,060
Take care.

54
00:03:20,780 --> 00:03:21,620
Dear.

55
00:03:23,220 --> 00:03:27,730
♪With spring flowers and autumn moon,
I searched the yard thoroughly♪

56
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:30,180
♪Before the wind comes,
they've already withered♪

57
00:03:30,180 --> 00:03:35,580
♪In this world, we read
each other's mind for nothing♪

58
00:03:36,410 --> 00:03:39,800
♪But no fate♪

59
00:03:42,410 --> 00:03:47,020
♪Too young to appreciate the moon;
Too full to suffer from lacking♪

60
00:03:47,020 --> 00:03:54,000
♪Never parted with the fleeting breeze
and people♪

61
00:03:55,670 --> 00:04:00,210
♪A glance that lingers♪

62
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:06,220
♪I wander alone in the wilderness,
with many years ahead♪

63
00:04:06,430 --> 00:04:10,040
♪Just waiting for you to see me♪

64
00:04:10,550 --> 00:04:15,790
♪Knowing this longing,
why do I write so resolutely♪

65
00:04:17,780 --> 00:04:18,620
Let's go.

66
00:04:18,620 --> 00:04:20,440
(Cui Mansion)

67
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:25,110
♪If the knot in my heart
waits for you to untangle♪

68
00:04:25,110 --> 00:04:29,720
♪The fallen leaves of memory
wait for you to pick up♪

69
00:04:30,090 --> 00:04:34,630
♪Waiting for that moment,
facing each other without words♪

70
00:04:34,630 --> 00:04:40,510
♪Like all the fleeting encounters
in this world♪

71
00:04:48,940 --> 00:04:50,250
- Enjoy, enjoy!
- Come on.

72
00:04:50,250 --> 00:04:51,560
- Please.
- Come on.

73
00:04:58,420 --> 00:04:59,860
- Please.
- Please.

74
00:05:00,260 --> 00:05:01,140
Xingzhou.

75
00:05:02,900 --> 00:05:04,100
A toast to you.

76
00:05:05,860 --> 00:05:06,860
Uncle,

77
00:05:07,780 --> 00:05:08,780
you're drunk.

78
00:05:09,340 --> 00:05:11,380
Why do you still call me uncle?

79
00:05:11,780 --> 00:05:14,060
You should call me father instead.

80
00:05:14,060 --> 00:05:15,020
You fool!

81
00:05:15,020 --> 00:05:16,220
How dare you be disrespectful?

82
00:05:16,980 --> 00:05:18,820
Why are you being so distant?

83
00:05:19,060 --> 00:05:20,860
It's more intimate this way.

84
00:05:21,140 --> 00:05:21,980
Right?

85
00:05:22,780 --> 00:05:23,700
This drunkard.

86
00:05:24,020 --> 00:05:25,260
Talking nonsense here.

87
00:05:26,100 --> 00:05:27,220
Let me apologize

88
00:05:27,460 --> 00:05:28,860
to you for him.

89
00:05:29,820 --> 00:05:31,980
The wedding is this month.

90
00:05:32,620 --> 00:05:34,020
I can't wait

91
00:05:34,020 --> 00:05:35,250
to hear Binglan

92
00:05:35,260 --> 00:05:36,780
call me mother.

93
00:05:37,220 --> 00:05:39,500
Xingzhou has waited three years

94
00:05:39,500 --> 00:05:41,380
to hear her call him honey.

95
00:05:41,390 --> 00:05:42,770
Isn't that right, Xingzhou?

96
00:05:43,830 --> 00:05:44,670
Honey.

97
00:05:54,100 --> 00:05:54,940
The poor child

98
00:05:55,140 --> 00:05:56,220
has been eagerly

99
00:05:56,420 --> 00:05:57,780
waiting to see Binglan.

100
00:06:00,740 --> 00:06:02,100
He can't see her for days.

101
00:06:02,380 --> 00:06:04,020
Once the six rituals are complete,

102
00:06:04,260 --> 00:06:05,580
on the day of the wedding,

103
00:06:05,580 --> 00:06:07,100
they'll finally meet.

104
00:06:08,340 --> 00:06:10,060
Our mansion is fortunate

105
00:06:10,300 --> 00:06:11,820
to have a princess like Binglan,

106
00:06:11,820 --> 00:06:12,940
from a matching family,

107
00:06:13,260 --> 00:06:14,900
with wisdom and grace.

108
00:06:15,100 --> 00:06:16,220
This is truly

109
00:06:16,220 --> 00:06:18,740
a perfect union and a grand celebration.

110
00:06:21,660 --> 00:06:23,300
You've always had your own ideas.

111
00:06:24,060 --> 00:06:25,500
How do you plan

112
00:06:25,700 --> 00:06:27,180
to organize your wedding?

113
00:06:32,220 --> 00:06:33,580
A wedding for Lord Huaiyang

114
00:06:34,420 --> 00:06:35,660
should be

115
00:06:36,620 --> 00:06:38,220
as grand

116
00:06:38,740 --> 00:06:40,220
and lively as possible.

117
00:06:40,740 --> 00:06:41,580
Yes.

118
00:06:41,740 --> 00:06:42,660
Come on.

119
00:06:42,820 --> 00:06:43,660
Let's drink.

120
00:06:44,180 --> 00:06:45,060
Let's drink.

121
00:06:47,500 --> 00:06:48,350
Congratulations!

122
00:06:48,350 --> 00:06:49,680
Thank you. Thank you.

123
00:06:53,060 --> 00:06:53,940
My Lord,

124
00:06:54,300 --> 00:06:56,820
here are wedding clothes in patterned silk,

125
00:06:57,140 --> 00:06:58,780
silk tapestry,

126
00:06:59,220 --> 00:07:01,500
feathered fabric,

127
00:07:01,740 --> 00:07:04,260
and gambiered Canton silk.

128
00:07:04,580 --> 00:07:06,940
Which one do you prefer?

129
00:07:10,900 --> 00:07:11,740
Any of them will do.

130
00:07:13,570 --> 00:07:14,410
Dried fruits.

131
00:07:14,660 --> 00:07:15,500
- Thanks.
- Take it.

132
00:07:16,930 --> 00:07:18,020
Look at these dried fruits.

133
00:07:18,030 --> 00:07:20,220
Madam, why are you suddenly buying fabric?

134
00:07:20,620 --> 00:07:21,780
To make clothes?

135
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:23,220
Not for clothes.

136
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,900
Dried fruits.

137
00:07:28,900 --> 00:07:32,140
(Fabric Store)

138
00:07:33,100 --> 00:07:33,940
Shopkeeper.

139
00:07:34,220 --> 00:07:35,060
Coming.

140
00:07:35,740 --> 00:07:36,580
Madam.

141
00:07:36,620 --> 00:07:38,660
I'd like to choose a red fabric
with gold embroidery

142
00:07:38,860 --> 00:07:40,180
that's resistant to decay.

143
00:07:40,180 --> 00:07:41,940
Red with gold. Resistant to decay.

144
00:07:42,260 --> 00:07:43,780
May I ask what it's for?

145
00:07:44,060 --> 00:07:44,900
Marriage certificate.

146
00:07:51,060 --> 00:07:51,900
My Lord?

147
00:07:54,060 --> 00:07:54,900
My Lord?

148
00:08:13,100 --> 00:08:13,940
It's done, My Lord.

149
00:08:55,020 --> 00:08:55,860
My Lord.

150
00:08:59,420 --> 00:09:01,660
This is the gift list sent by the steward.

151
00:09:01,660 --> 00:09:02,500
Please review it.

152
00:09:13,060 --> 00:09:15,940
(Pure Copper Buddha Statue,
Wang Ximeng's Landscape Painting)

153
00:09:15,940 --> 00:09:17,620
(Ginseng, Salvia, Fallopia multiflora)

154
00:09:18,300 --> 00:09:20,100
My Lord, is there anything else you need?

155
00:09:22,820 --> 00:09:23,980
A cart of high-end charcoal.

156
00:09:23,980 --> 00:09:24,820
Alright.

157
00:09:26,340 --> 00:09:27,700
And several hand warmers.

158
00:09:27,940 --> 00:09:28,780
Yes.

159
00:09:28,790 --> 00:09:30,580
And at least a month's supply

160
00:09:30,580 --> 00:09:31,980
of mugwort and garden balsam stem.

161
00:09:33,140 --> 00:09:34,900
Clothing, fur coats, felt socks, and shoes

162
00:09:35,210 --> 00:09:37,260
should be prepared after confirming the sizes

163
00:09:37,580 --> 00:09:38,460
with Nanny Li.

164
00:09:40,020 --> 00:09:40,900
My Lord,

165
00:09:41,540 --> 00:09:42,860
are you preparing for the wedding

166
00:09:42,860 --> 00:09:44,140
or settling...

167
00:09:46,180 --> 00:09:48,180
Or settling Ms. Liu?

168
00:09:53,140 --> 00:09:54,020
Rest assured, My Lord.

169
00:09:54,260 --> 00:09:56,060
I'll take care of these things.

170
00:09:56,460 --> 00:09:58,060
When Ms. Liu returns to Beizhou,

171
00:09:58,060 --> 00:09:59,620
Nanny Li and Fan Hu will look after her.

172
00:10:02,580 --> 00:10:03,420
Prepare the carriage.

173
00:10:04,140 --> 00:10:04,980
To Lingquan?

174
00:10:05,020 --> 00:10:05,900
To Zhao Quan's place.

175
00:10:06,940 --> 00:10:07,780
Yes.

176
00:10:10,740 --> 00:10:12,620
You're about to get married,

177
00:10:12,620 --> 00:10:13,780
winning the beauty.

178
00:10:14,180 --> 00:10:15,660
So why are you

179
00:10:15,660 --> 00:10:17,020
like a solitary figure?

180
00:10:23,180 --> 00:10:24,620
I envy you, though.

181
00:10:25,260 --> 00:10:26,380
At least Cousin Lian

182
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,740
is committed to you alone.

183
00:10:28,340 --> 00:10:29,180
No.

184
00:10:29,900 --> 00:10:31,820
She's committed to the position
as the Princess.

185
00:10:32,540 --> 00:10:33,700
That's still faithful.

186
00:10:34,620 --> 00:10:36,740
At least she didn't run away
before the wedding,

187
00:10:37,220 --> 00:10:39,100
leaving you in disgrace.

188
00:10:41,860 --> 00:10:43,900
If she had someone else in her heart,

189
00:10:44,300 --> 00:10:47,020
we'd truly be brothers in misfortune.

190
00:10:49,860 --> 00:10:50,700
Come here.

191
00:10:55,220 --> 00:10:56,380
Compared to you,

192
00:10:57,580 --> 00:10:58,980
I'm very content.

193
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:02,460
If you're content,

194
00:11:02,460 --> 00:11:03,860
why did you ask me to drink?

195
00:11:07,100 --> 00:11:08,020
I'm thirsty.

196
00:11:11,660 --> 00:11:13,100
Be honest with me.

197
00:11:13,540 --> 00:11:15,140
Do you feel guilty

198
00:11:15,140 --> 00:11:16,460
abandoning Liu Miantang?

199
00:11:17,820 --> 00:11:19,180
It was all just a show

200
00:11:19,180 --> 00:11:20,540
from the start.

201
00:11:20,980 --> 00:11:22,900
Now that everything is back on track.

202
00:11:22,900 --> 00:11:23,980
Why would I feel guilty?

203
00:11:23,980 --> 00:11:25,540
If I continued deceiving her...

204
00:11:25,540 --> 00:11:27,300
You're still guilty after all.

205
00:11:28,460 --> 00:11:29,300
True.

206
00:11:30,060 --> 00:11:32,140
Sending Liu Miantang back to her family,

207
00:11:32,500 --> 00:11:33,580
without holding her past,

208
00:11:33,580 --> 00:11:34,660
and freeing her,

209
00:11:34,860 --> 00:11:36,060
is indeed a great kindness

210
00:11:36,060 --> 00:11:37,420
from you.

211
00:11:38,740 --> 00:11:41,180
Anyway, Liu Miantang is happy.

212
00:11:41,540 --> 00:11:42,660
When she reaches Beizhou

213
00:11:42,940 --> 00:11:44,940
and receives that letter,

214
00:11:45,340 --> 00:11:47,380
learning the harsh truth,

215
00:11:47,620 --> 00:11:49,580
no matter how stormy her emotions,

216
00:11:49,580 --> 00:11:51,060
she won't be able to confront you.

217
00:11:51,820 --> 00:11:52,660
This move

218
00:11:53,260 --> 00:11:54,540
is truly brilliant.

219
00:11:55,820 --> 00:11:56,860
I admit it.

220
00:11:57,740 --> 00:12:00,500
I don't dare face her for a farewell,

221
00:12:00,500 --> 00:12:02,140
nor do I dare

222
00:12:02,140 --> 00:12:03,860
to explain everything in person.

223
00:12:06,500 --> 00:12:08,780
Then why did you let her go?

224
00:12:10,260 --> 00:12:12,020
Even if you kept her around,

225
00:12:12,020 --> 00:12:13,420
with Cousin Lian's temperament,

226
00:12:13,660 --> 00:12:15,300
there wouldn't be any trouble.

227
00:12:23,180 --> 00:12:24,540
Without any choice,

228
00:12:24,940 --> 00:12:26,740
the crabapple blossoms have fallen.

229
00:12:27,940 --> 00:12:29,580
The swallows return,

230
00:12:30,900 --> 00:12:33,460
familiar yet new.

231
00:12:50,620 --> 00:12:51,460
Madam,

232
00:12:52,260 --> 00:12:53,220
the wind is strong.

233
00:12:53,420 --> 00:12:54,260
With the medicine on,

234
00:12:54,460 --> 00:12:55,660
go rest quickly.

235
00:12:57,220 --> 00:12:58,060
Nanny Li.

236
00:12:58,740 --> 00:13:00,980
Did you prepare the robes

237
00:13:00,980 --> 00:13:02,500
and the charcoal stove as I asked?

238
00:13:05,700 --> 00:13:07,100
Yes, everything is ready.

239
00:13:07,980 --> 00:13:09,980
Tomorrow, Moru will deliver them

240
00:13:10,460 --> 00:13:11,420
to the master.

241
00:13:14,420 --> 00:13:16,620
This is the first time
he's been away for so long.

242
00:13:17,300 --> 00:13:18,180
I wonder

243
00:13:18,540 --> 00:13:20,780
if he's adjusting well to life on the mountain.

244
00:13:22,180 --> 00:13:23,220
I heard

245
00:13:23,220 --> 00:13:25,180
that Go masters tend to be quite eccentric.

246
00:13:25,580 --> 00:13:27,500
I hope he isn't having a hard time.

247
00:13:31,140 --> 00:13:34,580
Moru will take care of the master.

248
00:13:36,140 --> 00:13:37,580
Follow the master's wishes

249
00:13:38,020 --> 00:13:40,820
and go visit your family in Beizhou at ease.

250
00:13:40,980 --> 00:13:43,060
Spend some quality time at your grandpa's home.

251
00:13:43,660 --> 00:13:44,980
When that time comes...

252
00:13:46,700 --> 00:13:47,660
What?

253
00:13:48,500 --> 00:13:50,020
By then,

254
00:13:50,020 --> 00:13:51,180
the master

255
00:13:52,580 --> 00:13:54,020
should have returned home.

256
00:13:58,780 --> 00:13:59,620
Lately,

257
00:13:59,820 --> 00:14:01,660
my right eyelid keeps twitching.

258
00:14:02,060 --> 00:14:03,620
I can't shake this uneasy feeling.

259
00:14:04,100 --> 00:14:04,980
Well.

260
00:14:05,140 --> 00:14:07,180
You must be exhausted from working

261
00:14:07,380 --> 00:14:09,860
in the shop these past few days.

262
00:14:10,300 --> 00:14:12,100
You should rest earlier.

263
00:14:16,780 --> 00:14:17,620
Madam,

264
00:14:18,020 --> 00:14:20,500
the carriage and luggage for Beizhou

265
00:14:20,820 --> 00:14:22,300
are all prepared.

266
00:14:22,500 --> 00:14:23,420
We can

267
00:14:23,420 --> 00:14:25,060
set off anytime.

268
00:14:26,260 --> 00:14:27,700
I don't want to go to Beizhou now.

269
00:14:28,900 --> 00:14:29,780
Why not?

270
00:14:30,540 --> 00:14:31,420
There's still

271
00:14:32,260 --> 00:14:34,220
something unfinished here.

272
00:15:01,020 --> 00:15:02,740
I'm Shi Yikuan, Chief Commander of Qingzhou.

273
00:15:02,940 --> 00:15:03,780
Greetings, My Lord.

274
00:15:03,780 --> 00:15:04,620
General Shi.

275
00:15:05,340 --> 00:15:06,180
Please come in.

276
00:15:10,780 --> 00:15:12,820
(Soldier Documents)
My Lord.

277
00:15:14,180 --> 00:15:16,340
Thirteen thousand men have been enlisted.

278
00:15:16,940 --> 00:15:18,180
Those unwilling for service,

279
00:15:18,500 --> 00:15:20,060
of old age or frailty

280
00:15:20,060 --> 00:15:21,740
have been sent back home.

281
00:15:22,660 --> 00:15:23,500
From now on,

282
00:15:23,860 --> 00:15:24,740
our country

283
00:15:24,740 --> 00:15:26,900
is free from the worries of Mount Yang.

284
00:15:27,100 --> 00:15:27,940
General,

285
00:15:28,780 --> 00:15:30,020
your meticulous work

286
00:15:30,020 --> 00:15:31,020
has been invaluable.

287
00:15:32,460 --> 00:15:34,940
I will surely speak for you

288
00:15:35,060 --> 00:15:36,660
to the Empress Dowager.

289
00:15:36,980 --> 00:15:39,060
A promotion is in your future.

