00:15:53,660 --> 00:15:54,780
as a military man,

295
00:15:55,060 --> 00:15:56,900
if it weren't for your guidance,

296
00:15:57,260 --> 00:15:58,620
I wouldn't have thought

297
00:15:58,620 --> 00:16:00,260
of such a perfect plan

298
00:16:00,260 --> 00:16:02,580
to pacify Mount Yang and gain a son-in-law.

299
00:16:07,340 --> 00:16:09,500
However, Ziyu

