00:17:03,180 --> 00:17:04,260
When the time comes,

320
00:17:04,260 --> 00:17:05,900
General, you'll be a favored minister,

321
00:17:06,420 --> 00:17:07,420
and I

322
00:17:07,540 --> 00:17:09,100
