323
00:17:09,500 --> 00:17:11,380
For both public and personal reasons,

324
00:17:11,380 --> 00:17:12,300
our goals align,

325
00:17:13,700 --> 00:17:15,140
General.

326
00:17:17,500 --> 00:17:19,060
Our goals align.

327
00:17:21,660 --> 00:17:23,140
Miss, are you still managing?

328
