329
00:17:25,380 --> 00:17:26,700
- Careful yourself.
- Don't run!

330
00:17:26,700 --> 00:17:27,540
If it drops...

331
00:17:27,820 --> 00:17:29,260
- Slow down!
- Sorry!

332
00:17:29,260 --> 00:17:30,140
Sorry! Sorry!

333
00:17:30,140 --> 00:17:31,180
What should we do?

334
00:17:31,180 --> 00:17:32,540
Stop running!

335
00:17:36,060 --> 00:17:37,740
Mr. Ziyu.

336
00:17:38,580 --> 00:17:40,660
I thought I saw you earlier

337
00:17:41,140 --> 00:17:42,580
but wasn't sure.

338
00:17:44,820 --> 00:17:45,900
What a coincidence.

339
00:17:48,420 --> 00:17:49,740
You really like that crimson.

340
00:17:51,620 --> 00:17:52,460
You just bought it,

341
00:17:52,780 --> 00:17:53,740
and you're holding it.

342
00:17:54,580 --> 00:17:56,100
It's for my sister.

343
00:17:57,580 --> 00:17:58,540
What about yours?

344
00:18:02,020 --> 00:18:03,780
I have enough clothes.

345
00:18:03,780 --> 00:18:04,780
No need for more.

346
00:18:04,780 --> 00:18:06,140
I'll wait for my sister.

347
00:18:12,940 --> 00:18:14,220
- Help her with it.
- Yes.

348
00:18:16,100 --> 00:18:17,420
I wouldn't dare trouble you.

349
00:18:17,420 --> 00:18:18,980
