362
00:18:59,780 --> 00:19:01,140
Would you like to try some?

363
00:19:02,780 --> 00:19:03,820
Thank you.

364
00:19:04,180 --> 00:19:06,340
But my mother always taught me

365
00:19:06,340 --> 00:19:08,700
