366
00:19:10,740 --> 00:19:12,860
You should adhere to those teachings.

367
00:19:13,620 --> 00:19:14,820
Forgive my presumptuousness.

368
00:19:32,620 --> 00:19:33,620
Take it. Careful.

369
00:19:33,620 --> 00:19:34,460
