- Go.

370
00:19:34,660 --> 00:19:35,860
Let's go home and eat.

371
00:19:35,860 --> 00:19:37,060
Take a look.

372
00:19:42,280 --> 00:19:43,120
Come on.

373
00:19:44,900 --> 00:19:45,740
Want some?

374
00:19:45,740 --> 00:19:46,620
Yes.

375
00:19:47,660 --> 00:19:48,500
