376
00:19:48,660 --> 00:19:50,100
Take it over there.

377
00:19:50,620 --> 00:19:52,060
Thank you for your help today.

378
00:19:54,100 --> 00:19:54,940
Slow down.

379
00:19:55,300 --> 00:19:56,140
Zhuwen.

380
00:19:56,220 --> 00:19:57,140
What's this?

381
00:19:58,380 --> 00:20:00,340
Mr. Lu bought two bolts

382
00:20:00,340 --> 00:20:01,300
of fine patterned silk.

383
00:20:01,540 --> 00:20:02,620
I think they're

384
00:20:02,620 --> 00:20:04,060
prettier than that crimson one.

385
00:20:05,870 --> 00:20:07,200
I've heard that you're

386
00:20:07,200 --> 00:20:08,420
highly favored at home.

387
00:20:08,640 --> 00:20:09,940
I must do my best

388
00:20:10,220 --> 00:20:11,780
to ensure you aren't wronged.

389
00:20:15,380 --> 00:20:16,540
Don't lose the rouge

390
00:20:16,940 --> 00:20:17,900
you just bought.

391
00:20:21,420 --> 00:20:22,780
Thank you, Young Master.

392
00:20:29,860 --> 00:20:30,980
What...

393
00:20:31,100 --> 00:20:32,020
What are you doing?

394
00:20:32,580 --> 00:20:33,420
I...

395
