Maintain your distance.

396
00:20:35,620 --> 00:20:37,500
My sister is about to be married,

397
00:20:37,980 --> 00:20:38,860
and you can't afford

398
00:20:39,100 --> 00:20:40,180
to offend her fiance.

399
00:20:43,460 --> 00:20:44,300
Are you mad?

400
00:20:44,700 --> 00:20:46,220
How dare you walk with a strange man?

401
00:20:46,580 --> 00:20:48,300
- This...
- If that bandit sees this,

402
00:20:48,460 --> 00:20:50,100
who knows how he'll punish you?

403
00:20:50,100 --> 00:20:51,100
Sister, he...

404
00:20:52,860 --> 00:20:54,100
The bandit?

405
00:20:56,100 --> 00:20:58,220
Miss Shi, is that what you call me?

406
00:21:02,500 --> 00:21:03,460
Sister,

407
00:21:03,460 --> 00:21:04,980
this is Mr. Ziyu

408
00:21:04,980 --> 00:21:06,300
from Mount Yang.

409
00:21:18,180 --> 00:21:19,620
(Jinchen Tea)

410
00:21:25,900 --> 00:21:26,980
Congratulations, Miss.

411
00:21:27,380 --> 00:21:30,180
Your wish is finally coming true.

412
00:21:31,780 --> 00:21:33,140
At the auspicious hour today,

413
00:21:33,260 --> 00:21:35,300
the Lord will personally deliver the gift list,

414
00:21:35,420 --> 00:21:36,460
showing his respect

415
00:21:36,460 --> 00:21:38,220
and esteem for you.

416
00:21:38,220 --> 00:21:39,340
Cousin Xingzhou has always

417
00:21:39,340 --> 00:21:41,220
been thoughtful and considerate towards me.

418
00:21:41,380 --> 00:21:42,540
Of course.

419
00:21:42,940 --> 00:21:44,260
Once the gift list arrives,

420
00:21:44,540 --> 00:21:46,420
only the wedding ceremony remains.

421
00:21:46,900 --> 00:21:47,740
Miss,

422
00:21:47,940 --> 00:21:49,060
after today,

423
00:21:49,060 --> 00:21:50,260
you'll no longer be my lady.

424
00:21:50,500 --> 00:21:53,100
I will have to start calling you Princess.

425
00:21:59,100 --> 00:22:01,500
The auspicious hour approaches.
It's time to depart.

